  "analyst_note": "CVE-2022-20695: Authentication bypass in Cisco Wireless LAN Controller (WLC) management interface when RADIUS MAC authentication is enabled with a specific security configuration. CVSS 9.8. Affects Cisco WLC AireOS Software. If Cisco WLC management interface is internet-facing, this is a critical priority. Verify by checking if RADIUS MAC authentication with PAP is configured. Fixed: 8.10.162.0 for AireOS-based WLCs. Note: Cisco Catalyst 9800 series (IOS-XE based) are not affected.",
